        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This seems ok but a question is why this should be allowed? The point of `vim.diagnostic` is to provide a diagnostics framework. \r\n\r\nWhy should random diagnostics be allowed to override the diagnostic severity highlighting?  The user expects severities to have their configured highlighting.\r\n\r\nI think we should avoid adding random things like this until there is clear demand and a strong use-case.",
